\beta \in \mathbb{R}
T
  (1,-7)^T = \alpha (1,-1)^T + \beta (1,1)^T 
  T(1,-7)^T = T(\alpha(1,-1)^T + \beta(1,1)^T) = \alpha T(1,-1)^T + \beta T(1,1)^T = \ldots 
