  (1,-7)^T = \alpha (1,0)^T + \beta (0,1)^T 
  (1,-7)^T = \alpha (1,0)^T + \beta (0,1)^T = \alpha T(1,1)^T + \beta T(1,-1)^T = T(\alpha(1,1)^T + \beta(1,-1)^T) = \ldots 
